<div class="page-header">
  <h1>Buttons <small>grouping buttons</small></h1>
</div>

<p>
  Buttons can also be grouped together into individual groups, or full toolbars.  For individual button groups, you simply wrap a series of button elements in a div with the 
  <code>btn-group</code> class applied to it as follows:
</p>

<div class="btn-group">
  <button class="btn btn-info">Button Number 1</button>
  <button class="btn btn-info">Button Number 2</button>
  <button class="btn btn-info">Button Number 3</button>
  <button class="btn btn-info">Button Number 4</button>
</div>
<br/><br/>

<pre>
  &lt;div class="btn-group"&gt;
    &lt;button class="btn btn-info"&gt;Button Number 1&lt;/button&gt;
    &lt;button class="btn btn-info"&gt;Button Number 2&lt;/button&gt;
    &lt;button class="btn btn-info"&gt;Button Number 3&lt;/button&gt;
    &lt;button class="btn btn-info"&gt;Button Number 4&lt;/button&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;
</pre>

<p>
  To combine button groups into a toolbar is as simple as wrapping your individual button groups in a div with the <code>btn-toolbar</code> class applied to it as follows:
</p>

<div class="btn-toolbar">
  <div class="btn-group">
    <button class="btn btn-info">1</button>
    <button class="btn btn-info">2</button>
    <button class="btn btn-info">3</button>
    <button class="btn btn-info">4</button>
  </div>

  <div class="btn-group">
    <button class="btn btn-warning">5</button>
    <button class="btn btn-warning">6</button>
    <button class="btn btn-warning">7</button>
    <button class="btn btn-warning">8</button>
  </div>

  <div class="btn-group">
    <button class="btn btn-success">9</button>
  </div>
</div>

<pre>
  &lt;div class="btn-toolbar"&gt;
    &lt;div class="btn-group"&gt;
      &lt;button class="btn btn-info"&gt;1&lt;/button&gt;
      &lt;button class="btn btn-info"&gt;2&lt;/button&gt;
      &lt;button class="btn btn-info"&gt;3&lt;/button&gt;
      &lt;button class="btn btn-info"&gt;4&lt;/button&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;

    &lt;div class="btn-group"&gt;
      &lt;button class="btn btn-warning"&gt;5&lt;/button&gt;
      &lt;button class="btn btn-warning"&gt;6&lt;/button&gt;
      &lt;button class="btn btn-warning"&gt;7&lt;/button&gt;
      &lt;button class="btn btn-warning"&gt;8&lt;/button&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;

    &lt;div class="btn-group"&gt;
      &lt;button class="btn btn-success"&gt;9&lt;/button&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;
</pre>
